                <h3 class="subheading">Design Philosophy: Commanding Presence and Bolder Stance</h3>
                <p>The moment one lays eyes on the all-new Seltos, it's clear that Kia's designers have embraced an aggressive, modern aesthetic while maintaining the vehicle's instantly recognizable silhouette. The exterior design has been meticulously re-sculpted, giving the Seltos a larger, more planted, and commanding presence on the road.</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">The Kia Digital Tiger Face</span></p>
                <p>At the heart of the front-end redesign is the <span class="font-weight-700">Commanding Kia Digital Tiger Face with a Black High Glossy Grille. </span>This revised grille design is more angular and prominent, seamlessly flowing into the signature lighting elements. The headlamps, now featuring<span class="font-weight-700"> Intense Ice Cube LED Projection Headlamps with Star Map LED DRLs,</span> create a distinct visual signature both day and night.</p>
                <p>The front bumper is reworked to appear more robust, incorporating<span class="font-weight-700"> High-Clarity LED Front Fog Lamps and Robust Front & Rear Skid Plates with Dark Gunmetal Finish, </span>signaling its readiness for adventure, whether navigating city traffic or exploring the open highway.</p>
