                <h3 class="subheading">Interior and Comfort: The Digital Cockpit Experience</h3>
                <p>Stepping inside the all-new Seltos is akin to entering a premium lounge, designed with a focus on cutting-edge technology, superior comfort, and exceptional fit and finish. The extended wheelbase has ensured a roomier cabin with more legroom for all occupants, significantly boosting comfort on longer journeys.</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700"> The Trinity Panoramic Display</span></p>
                <p>The centrepiece of the completely revamped dashboard is the stunning<span class="font-weight-700">  Trinity Panoramic Display,</span> a single, integrated curved panel housing two high-definition 12.3-inch screens. This magnificent digital setup combines the fully digital driver’s instrument cluster and the main infotainment and navigation touchscreen, offering crisp, easy-to-read graphics and a truly futuristic feel.</p>
                <p>The infotainment system supports the latest connectivity features, including Kia Connect 2.0 with a complimentary 3-year subscription, over-the-air (OTA) software updates, and seamless integration with <span class="font-weight-700"> Wireless Android Auto and Apple CarPlay</span>.</p>
                <p>Below the main display, the climate control system is elegantly managed via a separate <span class="font-weight-700"> 5-inch climate control screen, </span>ensuring a cleaner, more organized central console. For ultimate passenger comfort, the Seltos also features a<span class="font-weight-700">  Dual-Zone Fully Automatic Air Conditioner,</span> allowing the driver and front passenger to set their own preferred temperatures.</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700"> Premium Features for Utmost Convenience</span></p>
                <p>Kia has loaded the new Seltos with an array of comfort and convenience features that truly set it apart:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700"> Power-Adjustable and Ventilated Seats: </span>The top-tier variants offer a <span class="font-weight-700"> 10-way Power-Adjustable Driver Seat with Memory Function</span> and a welcome retract feature for ease of entry and exit. Coupled with <span class="font-weight-700"> Ventilated Front Seats, </span>the Seltos makes driving in hot weather a much more pleasant experience.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700"> Bose Premium Sound System: </span>Music lovers will appreciate the immersive audio experience provided by the<span class="font-weight-700">  8-speaker Bose Premium Sound System.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700"> Dual Pane Panoramic Sunroof: </span>The addition of a <span class="font-weight-700"> Dual Pane Panoramic Sunroof </span>drastically enhances the sense of space and airiness in the cabin, allowing light to flood the interiors and making every drive a delightful experience.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700"> Ambient Lighting:</span> The cabin is further enhanced by <span class="font-weight-700"> 64-colour Ambient Lighting, </span>which can be customized to match the driver’s mood, providing a truly personalized environment.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700"> Smart Utility: </span>Practicality is maintained with features like a <span class="font-weight-700"> Wireless Phone Charger, </span>multiple USB-C charging ports for both rows, and useful elements like rear door sunshades and a tilt and telescopic steering wheel.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3 class="subheading">Impressive Performance: Engines and Driving Dynamics</h3>
                <div class="row m-b20">
